data.description: Welcome home to this all brick beautiful ranch home in the  middle of a nice neighborhood. Don't want to miss on this wonderful home with 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. Main floor family room with fireplace to cozy up on a cold night. Beautiful kitchen that features stainless appliances, granite countertops and skylight that brings in plenty of natural light. Master bedroom that has your own private bathroom.   Backyard has plenty of room to entertain guests and family with big deck and big lawn for the kids to  Play on. Yard has a shed to store lawn furniture, lawnmower and many more things. 2 car attached garage.   Don't want to miss out on your dreams home! Short Sale. As-IS property! Schedule your appointment now!
